Description: Open-source multilingual AI agent platform
 ARGO is an open-source AI agent platform built from two components:
 argo-core, a small Rust HTTP gateway (Axum + Tokio), and argo-brain,
 a Python brain that runs the agent loop, tools and memory. The two
 communicate over a Unix domain socket using line-delimited JSON.
 .
 ARGO is specially optimised for Central Asian languages and DevOps
 workflows, and is designed for sovereign, self-hosted deployment.
 .
 This package installs both components and a systemd service for the
 argo-core gateway, which listens on HTTP port 8000.
